HEADWORD: Incremate
<hw>In"cre*mate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>in-</ets> in + <ets>cremate</ets>.]</ety> <def>To consume or reduce
